WEBVTT

00:00:10.060 --> 00:00:11.060
Hurry up.

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:13.000
You need to get ready.

00:00:14.140 --> 00:00:15.890
Okay, okay, I'm getting up.

00:00:16.820 --> 00:00:18.860
That's the third time you've said that.

00:00:31.110 --> 00:00:32.480
You're way too excited.

00:00:35.340 --> 00:00:36.540
Of course I am.

00:00:37.700 --> 00:00:39.580
This is our very first trip together.

00:00:41.773 --> 00:00:43.293
You're acting like it's a school trip.

00:00:44.180 --> 00:00:46.040
How long ago was that?

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:48.600
Seriously,

00:00:48.766 --> 00:00:54.960
you have no idea how much
I've been looking forward to this.

00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:57.240
I know.

00:00:58.340 --> 00:00:59.780
I've been looking forward to it too.

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:03.080
Is that so?

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:21.800
(Special Episode: What if...
where would we be now?)

00:01:32.380 --> 00:01:33.380
Wow, that's a lot.

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.200
Don't you love them?

00:01:36.300 --> 00:01:37.300
It is a lot, though.

00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:33.400
The tea is ready. I'll leave it here.

00:02:33.640 --> 00:02:34.680
Okay.

00:02:35.300 --> 00:02:36.300
Thanks.

00:02:47.420 --> 00:02:50.000
How long has it been
since we last went on a trip?

00:02:50.866 --> 00:02:52.746
I heard you traveled a lot in college.

00:02:53.130 --> 00:02:55.800
Ah, did Futami tell you that?

00:02:56.660 --> 00:02:57.660
Something like that.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:03.150
He didn't say anything weird, did he?

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:05.180
Do you have something to hide?

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:06.970
No way, of course not.

00:03:09.880 --> 00:03:12.440
On the surface, it's a
casual trip with friends,

00:03:12.810 --> 00:03:14.410
but you were actually hitting on people?

00:03:14.730 --> 00:03:15.730
What?!

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:19.040
You seem really
experienced in a lot of ways.

00:03:19.070 --> 00:03:20.256
Like making all these arrangements.

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:23.160
No, I'm not that experienced...

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:24.580
You clearly are.

00:03:25.300 --> 00:03:27.420
Whether it's hitting on
people or sleeping with guys.

00:03:29.710 --> 00:03:32.280
You even said before that
sleeping with guys is easier.

00:03:32.460 --> 00:03:35.460
No, I was just talking nonsense back then.

00:03:35.500 --> 00:03:36.670
In reality, I didn't...

00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:38.460
But that wasn't a lie, was it?

00:03:40.420 --> 00:03:41.430
Back then...

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:44.720
I wanted to forget about you.

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:47.950
I did go through a self-destructive phase.

00:03:48.350 --> 00:03:49.350
What?

00:03:50.350 --> 00:03:55.190
I decided to give up
on you after high school,

00:03:57.650 --> 00:04:00.060
but in the end, I just couldn't forget you.

00:04:01.300 --> 00:04:02.659
If things were like that,

00:04:02.660 --> 00:04:04.460
you should've just contacted me.

00:04:04.990 --> 00:04:07.000
I just wanted to move on in my own way.

00:04:07.370 --> 00:04:10.570
Making decisions all on your
own is a bad habit of yours.

00:04:11.860 --> 00:04:12.860
But,

00:04:12.940 --> 00:04:15.210
since I was the reason
you were self-destructive,

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:17.040
I'll forgive you.

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:22.480
What if...

00:04:23.960 --> 00:04:27.030
we had stayed in touch after high school?

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.510
Where would we be right now?

00:04:31.820 --> 00:04:32.820
Who knows?

00:04:36.810 --> 00:04:37.910
What about you, Zen?

00:04:39.270 --> 00:04:40.710
After you started college,

00:04:41.190 --> 00:04:43.460
did you ever think about contacting me?

00:04:44.660 --> 00:04:45.670
Well,

00:04:46.530 --> 00:04:47.660
maybe I was waiting.

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:49.580
Waiting for you to reach out.

00:04:49.930 --> 00:04:52.260
Wait, seriously?

00:04:52.450 --> 00:04:53.860
But back then,

00:04:53.870 --> 00:04:55.810
you didn't seem interested in me at all.

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:58.000
You're getting ruder by the second.

00:04:58.220 --> 00:05:00.050
Have you even been listening to me?

00:05:01.300 --> 00:05:03.340
Don't jump to conclusions
about my feelings.

00:05:03.880 --> 00:05:05.480
You always jump to your own conclusions.

00:05:05.590 --> 00:05:06.890
Huh...

00:05:07.640 --> 00:05:10.180
Then why are you only telling me this now?

00:05:10.470 --> 00:05:11.770
Because you only asked me today.

00:05:13.270 --> 00:05:16.229
If we had gotten in touch sooner,

00:05:16.230 --> 00:05:19.870
would we have ended up like this sooner?

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:26.300
Ah...

00:05:28.880 --> 00:05:30.950
I wish I could go back in time.

00:05:31.700 --> 00:05:33.540
Then we'll just have to
make up for lost time.

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:38.600
After all, we have plenty of time
to spend together from now on.

00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:43.760
True.

00:05:49.390 --> 00:05:51.200
This feels so good.

00:05:51.640 --> 00:05:52.810
Hot springs are the best.

00:06:34.140 --> 00:06:35.160
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

00:06:40.020 --> 00:06:41.020
Ah, that's good.

00:06:43.070 --> 00:06:45.110
Yeah, this is delicious.

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:49.480
Delicious.

00:06:49.660 --> 00:06:51.160
It's incredibly delicious this way.

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:52.920
Oh?

00:06:54.640 --> 00:06:56.660
You really know your stuff.

00:06:58.330 --> 00:06:59.460
- Is it good?
- Yeah.

00:07:15.920 --> 00:07:17.680
Ah, it's so good.

00:07:20.060 --> 00:07:22.560
"Things I want to do with Zen" list.

00:07:23.150 --> 00:07:24.790
We finally checked off the first one.

00:07:25.580 --> 00:07:26.580
What is that?

00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:28.479
How many things are on there?

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.300
Huh?

00:07:29.300 --> 00:07:30.300
A lot.

00:07:32.410 --> 00:07:33.410
Watching movies,

00:07:33.740 --> 00:07:36.490
night drives, camping,

00:07:37.080 --> 00:07:38.740
fishing, and traveling abroad.

00:07:39.980 --> 00:07:40.980
I forgot.

00:07:41.500 --> 00:07:43.460
Our interests don't match at all.

00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:45.850
Because you're an indoor person.

00:07:47.180 --> 00:07:48.820
Looks like I need to build up my stamina.

00:07:49.760 --> 00:07:51.930
After all, I've never
beaten you in any sports.

00:07:51.970 --> 00:07:53.090
Just to beat me?

00:07:54.550 --> 00:07:55.850
So I can keep up with you.

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:04.800
Hey,

00:08:04.980 --> 00:08:06.620
watch how fast you're drinking.

00:08:07.070 --> 00:08:08.830
It'll be a problem if
you fall asleep first.

00:08:08.933 --> 00:08:11.143
You weren't planning on
letting me sleep anyway, right?

00:08:12.700 --> 00:08:13.920
You know me well.

00:08:14.110 --> 00:08:15.740
You're just too easy to read.

00:08:16.830 --> 00:08:17.830
In that case,

00:08:18.646 --> 00:08:21.416
guess what I want to do right now.

00:08:24.520 --> 00:08:25.520
Well...

00:08:33.290 --> 00:08:34.290
Here.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:39.360
It's a bit early, but happy birthday.

00:08:40.940 --> 00:08:41.940
Thank you.

00:08:42.850 --> 00:08:43.850
Hm?

00:08:44.660 --> 00:08:46.399
Were you expecting something else just now?

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:47.400
No, I wasn't.

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:49.020
Can I open it now?

00:08:49.070 --> 00:08:50.070
Go ahead.

00:09:00.790 --> 00:09:03.330
I thought an accessory would be nice,

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:06.220
but is it too ordinary?

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:08.499
Knowing you,

00:09:08.500 --> 00:09:10.480
I actually thought you
might have gotten a ring.

00:09:12.300 --> 00:09:13.590
Then I'll go get my gift too.

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:17.340
Well, though I think you probably
already know what's inside.

00:09:19.520 --> 00:09:21.530
So a ring would've been okay...

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:24.000
Here.

00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:31.610
Well, thank you again.

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:34.309
But for this gift,

00:09:34.310 --> 00:09:36.410
I was really put through
the wringer by someone.

00:09:37.340 --> 00:09:38.340
I said I was sorry.

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:40.320
Hey, can I open it now?

00:09:40.330 --> 00:09:41.790
No, open it later.

00:09:41.910 --> 00:09:42.910
Hm?

00:09:43.620 --> 00:09:46.370
If we don't hurry, I'm
really going to fall asleep.

00:09:48.170 --> 00:09:49.170
What's this?

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.500
You're being quite bold today.

00:09:51.980 --> 00:09:54.320
Don't think you're the only
one who's been holding back.

00:09:57.180 --> 00:09:58.180
Ryo.

00:09:58.430 --> 00:09:59.760
Happy birthday.

00:10:06.880 --> 00:10:07.890
Thank you.

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:16.610
Who is it?

00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:18.860
At this hour on a Saturday.

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:23.200
It's Futami.

00:10:25.800 --> 00:10:26.870
Can we just ignore him?

00:10:27.210 --> 00:10:28.210
Let it go.

00:10:28.320 --> 00:10:30.290
It's been ringing
constantly since last night.

00:10:32.060 --> 00:10:34.250
Well, we did part on bad terms...

00:10:35.090 --> 00:10:38.540
Ryo is my boyfriend.

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:48.400
You should probably answer it.

00:10:49.020 --> 00:10:51.660
I don't want to keep being interrupted.

00:10:53.150 --> 00:10:54.400
True.

00:10:55.300 --> 00:10:56.540
Ah, he answered! Wait...

00:10:56.780 --> 00:10:57.470
Hello?

00:10:57.480 --> 00:10:59.240
I didn't hear anything
about you two dating.

00:10:59.610 --> 00:11:00.700
Sorry, sorry.

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:02.120
Yeah.

00:12:20.230 --> 00:12:21.740
Let me get my revenge.

00:12:22.990 --> 00:12:24.440
I knew you'd say that.

00:12:24.990 --> 00:12:26.590
So, what are the rules?

00:12:26.660 --> 00:12:29.450
The first one to give in loses.

00:12:30.910 --> 00:12:34.140
Still the same silly game as always.

00:12:34.250 --> 00:12:35.250
Yeah.

00:12:36.910 --> 00:12:39.000
Being with you,
I feel like I'm getting dumber too.

00:12:40.730 --> 00:12:42.210
It's a bit late to realize that now.

00:12:44.730 --> 00:12:46.970
Then I guess I'll just have to accept it.

00:13:18.550 --> 00:13:20.130
You wearing a yukata is totally unfair.

00:13:21.380 --> 00:13:22.460
You too.

00:13:52.990 --> 00:13:57.000
Wow, I feel alive again.

00:13:57.950 --> 00:13:59.810
I won that game just now.

00:14:00.770 --> 00:14:03.020
Okay, okay, I get it.

00:14:03.710 --> 00:14:04.710
So?

00:14:05.170 --> 00:14:06.570
What does the winner want me to do?

00:14:14.590 --> 00:14:16.450
Should we move in together?

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:19.560
What?

00:14:20.310 --> 00:14:22.220
The winner's word is absolute, right?

00:14:22.610 --> 00:14:23.610
Huh?

00:14:23.780 --> 00:14:24.780
Wait...

00:14:25.110 --> 00:14:28.810
Hold on... Do you mean
we're moving in together?

00:14:28.850 --> 00:14:29.850
Yeah.

00:14:29.910 --> 00:14:32.369
We can stay at one of our places for now.

00:14:32.370 --> 00:14:34.360
Ah... wait, wait.

00:14:36.120 --> 00:14:37.120
Uh... well,

00:14:37.580 --> 00:14:38.780
why so sudden?

00:14:38.800 --> 00:14:39.870
It's not sudden at all.

00:14:40.250 --> 00:14:41.850
I've been thinking about it for a while.

00:14:43.136 --> 00:14:45.696
I don't like growing apart just
because we can't see each other.

00:14:45.920 --> 00:14:49.080
And I want to spend more time with you.

00:14:50.543 --> 00:14:51.543
Zen.

00:14:52.890 --> 00:14:54.969
Are you serious about this?

00:14:54.970 --> 00:14:56.870
How could I joke about something like this?

00:14:59.270 --> 00:15:00.790
What about you? Do you want to or not?

00:15:02.463 --> 00:15:06.783
Of course I do. That goes without saying.

00:15:08.590 --> 00:15:10.359
Oh my god, seriously?

00:15:10.360 --> 00:15:13.309
This is the best surprise gift ever.

00:15:13.310 --> 00:15:14.490
You're exaggerating.

00:15:14.950 --> 00:15:16.789
I'm holding you to what you just said.

00:15:16.790 --> 00:15:19.369
You can't back out now.

00:15:19.370 --> 00:15:21.419
That would be cheating.

00:15:21.420 --> 00:15:23.560
Don't go making up new rules.

00:15:24.170 --> 00:15:25.500
You'd better be prepared.

00:15:26.170 --> 00:15:27.860
My love is pretty heavy, you know.

00:15:28.010 --> 00:15:29.320
Maybe for now.

00:15:30.680 --> 00:15:31.680
Still,

00:15:32.170 --> 00:15:33.760
I'll catch up to you in no time anyway.

00:15:47.280 --> 00:15:49.110
I'll contact them first then.

00:15:49.320 --> 00:15:50.450
Thank you.

00:15:50.570 --> 00:15:52.359
Then I'll leave the scheduling to you.

00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:53.170
Will do!

00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:55.800
- Onishi, print this for me.
- Sure.

00:16:11.070 --> 00:16:13.139
I've put together the client's info.

00:16:13.140 --> 00:16:14.590
Let's divide and conquer.

00:16:14.630 --> 00:16:15.630
Okay.

00:16:15.850 --> 00:16:16.899
Oh, Minamide-san.

00:16:16.900 --> 00:16:18.669
Please help out Konishi and Higashino.

00:16:18.670 --> 00:16:19.670
Sure thing.

00:16:56.390 --> 00:16:57.550
It's too flashy.

00:16:57.640 --> 00:16:59.059
Yeah, it's so cute.

00:16:59.060 --> 00:17:00.639
It's weird, right?

00:17:00.640 --> 00:17:01.989
This is definitely cute.

00:17:01.990 --> 00:17:02.990
But you're cute too.

00:17:11.610 --> 00:17:13.790
Mmm, this is delicious.

00:17:35.070 --> 00:17:36.070
Well, everyone,

00:17:36.590 --> 00:17:38.950
Congratulations again. Thank
you for your hard work lately.

00:17:39.410 --> 00:17:40.180
Cheers!

00:17:40.181 --> 00:17:42.560
Cheers!

00:17:51.410 --> 00:17:54.510
Ah.

00:17:55.570 --> 00:17:56.910
That was a total whirlwind.

00:17:56.950 --> 00:17:58.609
Man, I thought I was
going to die of exhaustion.

00:17:58.610 --> 00:18:01.130
Seriously. The last two
weeks are a complete blur.

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:03.920
It's rare to have a project that
requires the entire sales department.

00:18:04.010 --> 00:18:05.290
I'm just glad it all worked out.

00:18:05.870 --> 00:18:06.870
As for me,

00:18:07.090 --> 00:18:09.476
my sister just had to get
married right in the middle of this.

00:18:09.500 --> 00:18:11.380
That must have been rough.

00:18:12.610 --> 00:18:14.079
Even when we were so busy,

00:18:14.080 --> 00:18:16.830
I kept getting dragged into
helping with this and that.

00:18:16.850 --> 00:18:17.530
But still,

00:18:17.531 --> 00:18:20.010
seeing the actual
wedding was really moving.

00:18:20.970 --> 00:18:22.209
What about you, Yotsuya-san?

00:18:22.210 --> 00:18:22.870
Huh?

00:18:22.870 --> 00:18:23.410
Oh.

00:18:23.450 --> 00:18:24.220
Your girlfriend.

00:18:24.450 --> 00:18:25.969
Any plans on getting married?

00:18:25.970 --> 00:18:27.090
Yeah!

00:18:27.170 --> 00:18:29.810
You too, Shito-san! Aren't you
guys already moving in together?

00:18:32.360 --> 00:18:33.360
Well...

00:18:33.940 --> 00:18:35.690
I am thinking about it.

00:18:36.370 --> 00:18:38.239
Ooh!

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:39.680
What about you, Shito-san?

00:18:39.770 --> 00:18:43.240
- True...
- But marriage is a huge step.

00:18:43.290 --> 00:18:45.550
It's not something you decide overnight.

00:18:45.580 --> 00:18:47.569
There's still a lot of prep work to do.

00:18:47.570 --> 00:18:49.569
Of course I'm considering it.

00:18:49.570 --> 00:18:51.789
Ooh!

00:18:51.790 --> 00:18:55.410
From the moment we started dating,

00:18:56.090 --> 00:18:57.630
I was already prepared to marry.

00:19:05.450 --> 00:19:06.930
What's with that look on your face?

00:19:07.530 --> 00:19:08.530
Hmph.

00:19:08.690 --> 00:19:10.110
Now you've got me curious.

00:19:10.770 --> 00:19:13.860
What exactly do you love about each other?

00:19:14.110 --> 00:19:15.480
Give us all the details.

00:19:16.280 --> 00:19:17.899
Well...

00:19:17.922 --> 00:19:22.342
There are many things,
but I guess it's everything.

00:19:25.150 --> 00:19:27.130
It's about time you showed us a photo.

00:19:27.210 --> 00:19:29.269
Shito-san, come on, show her off a bit.

00:19:29.270 --> 00:19:31.309
- How could you say something like that?
- Oh, come on!

00:19:31.310 --> 00:19:32.032
No way.

00:19:32.056 --> 00:19:34.249
What is up with that
complicated look on your face?

00:19:34.250 --> 00:19:36.840
- Are you jealous?
- Why would I be jealous?

00:19:37.800 --> 00:19:39.010
I'm totally jealous.

00:19:40.630 --> 00:19:42.279
Introduce me to someone too!

00:19:42.280 --> 00:19:43.709
Isn't there anyone good?

00:19:43.710 --> 00:19:44.810
See?

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:49.390
You always say that.

00:19:49.890 --> 00:19:50.890
You've got it wrong.

00:19:51.110 --> 00:19:52.710
But...

00:19:52.910 --> 00:19:54.730
Shima-san, is that how it is?

00:20:10.330 --> 00:20:14.370
You were just gushing about your
girlfriend with a huge smile on your face.

00:20:15.050 --> 00:20:16.140
Okay, okay, I'm sorry.

00:20:17.190 --> 00:20:18.390
I got a little carried away.

00:20:19.630 --> 00:20:20.630
And then?

00:20:21.530 --> 00:20:23.340
All this talk about marriage...

00:20:24.300 --> 00:20:26.220
I don't recall ever getting
a proposal from you.

00:20:26.630 --> 00:20:27.630
Well, that's...

00:20:30.330 --> 00:20:32.090
But I really am thinking
about it seriously.

00:20:33.330 --> 00:20:34.410
Hmm...

00:20:36.570 --> 00:20:41.080
Zen always includes me in his future plans

00:20:41.820 --> 00:20:43.820
and talks to me about it so sincerely.

00:20:45.170 --> 00:20:46.249
Did I?

00:20:46.250 --> 00:20:47.250
Yeah.

00:20:50.030 --> 00:20:55.030
When you said you were prepared
from the moment we started dating,

00:20:56.290 --> 00:20:57.630
that was incredibly cool.

00:20:59.710 --> 00:21:01.650
I really love that about you.

00:21:06.430 --> 00:21:08.860
But if I could be a little greedy,

00:21:10.890 --> 00:21:13.300
I'd actually love to hear what
exactly you love about me.

00:21:14.670 --> 00:21:17.830
That kind of stuff is meant to be said
in private, when it's just the two of us.

00:21:18.150 --> 00:21:21.440
Well, our sales
performance tied this quarter.

00:21:22.490 --> 00:21:23.490
Huh?

00:21:23.630 --> 00:21:24.630
Nothing.

00:21:25.510 --> 00:21:29.650
I was going to make you
list ten things you love about me.

00:21:32.330 --> 00:21:34.330
Looks like I'll have to
redeem myself next year.

00:21:35.870 --> 00:21:36.880
Good luck with that.

00:21:37.920 --> 00:21:39.020
I will.

00:21:40.530 --> 00:21:43.010
It would bother me if you said
you didn't have a rival anymore.

00:21:43.710 --> 00:21:45.499
Are you still holding a grudge over that?

00:21:45.500 --> 00:21:51.370
Because I want to keep
being your rival forever.

00:21:52.930 --> 00:21:54.610
You don't need to worry about that at all.

00:21:57.030 --> 00:21:59.350
Because we've long since
become more than just rivals.

00:22:07.550 --> 00:22:09.310
How you never compromise on your work.

00:22:10.950 --> 00:22:11.950
Huh?

00:22:12.580 --> 00:22:13.580
What?

00:22:13.930 --> 00:22:17.370
Since it's a tie, let's cut
it in half and name five.

00:22:19.250 --> 00:22:20.250
Things I love about you.

00:22:25.530 --> 00:22:26.760
You have to say them too.

00:22:30.810 --> 00:22:32.730
How surprisingly easy
it is to make you jealous.

00:22:32.760 --> 00:22:33.780
What?

00:22:36.070 --> 00:22:37.876
How you're not cute at
all when you're jealous.

00:22:37.900 --> 00:22:39.810
How you get serious
over the smallest things.

00:22:40.610 --> 00:22:41.870
How you hate to lose.

00:22:41.940 --> 00:22:43.210
You're the exact same way.

00:22:47.050 --> 00:22:48.110
Next.

00:22:52.450 --> 00:22:54.070
How when I'm with you,

00:22:55.370 --> 00:22:58.320
I feel like everything will be fine
no matter what happens.

00:23:04.010 --> 00:23:05.790
And how you love me way too much.

00:23:07.970 --> 00:23:09.329
Okay, I'm out of ideas. We're done.

00:23:09.330 --> 00:23:10.549
That was only four.

00:23:10.550 --> 00:23:12.529
- I really can't think of any more.
- No way.

00:23:12.530 --> 00:23:13.450
There must be at least one more.

00:23:13.451 --> 00:23:15.670
- My mind is blank.
- You jerk.

00:23:16.330 --> 00:23:17.580
- Busted.
- Shut up.

00:23:19.520 --> 00:23:24.530
I never thought that
after we became a couple,

00:23:24.570 --> 00:23:29.770
we'd actually be telling each other
what we love about one another like this.

00:23:31.550 --> 00:23:34.130
Especially since we had the worst start.

00:23:34.830 --> 00:23:36.410
I said I was sorry.

00:23:38.690 --> 00:23:41.890
But no matter what our relationship was,

00:23:43.210 --> 00:23:44.690
ever since high school,

00:23:46.190 --> 00:23:48.020
being with you has
always been the most fun.

00:23:50.863 --> 00:23:51.963
As for me,

00:23:54.376 --> 00:23:57.936
I love who I am when I'm with you the most.

00:24:03.210 --> 00:24:06.000
Alright, then that's the fifth one.

00:24:13.290 --> 00:24:14.290
Hey.

00:24:14.890 --> 00:24:16.650
That was so sudden!
We're outside, you idiot.

00:24:20.790 --> 00:24:21.990
You make me act like an idiot.

00:24:31.510 --> 00:24:32.590
For me,

00:24:35.170 --> 00:24:36.970
ever since I started dating you,

00:24:42.020 --> 00:24:44.380
everything that's happened
has been like a beautiful dream.

00:24:50.490 --> 00:24:51.490
In that case,

00:24:53.170 --> 00:24:55.970
we should keep turning
these dreams into reality.

00:25:13.090 --> 00:25:14.090
Are you cold?

00:25:17.890 --> 00:25:18.890
I'm fine.

00:25:20.550 --> 00:25:22.270
Because you're so warm.

00:25:36.320 --> 00:25:37.370
What is it?

00:25:40.810 --> 00:25:41.850
I love you.

00:25:49.670 --> 00:25:51.170
What's with that look on your face?

00:25:56.090 --> 00:25:58.320
You really do love me.

00:26:04.090 --> 00:26:06.020
Just saying that isn't enough.

00:26:12.450 --> 00:26:13.730
I love you.

00:26:15.570 --> 00:26:16.590
From now on,

00:26:19.280 --> 00:26:20.320
for the rest of our lives.

00:26:22.580 --> 00:26:23.660
That's pretty heavy.

00:26:25.120 --> 00:26:27.000
But you'll accept all of it, right?

00:26:29.790 --> 00:26:30.840
Of course I will.

00:26:43.270 --> 00:26:44.430
Ready, set...

00:26:47.070 --> 00:26:48.070
Huh?

00:26:51.320 --> 00:26:52.670
What is that in your hand...?

00:26:53.930 --> 00:26:55.296
What about you? What's that in your hand?

00:26:55.320 --> 00:26:56.900
What else could it be...?

00:26:58.430 --> 00:26:59.870
Obviously, it's for a proposal...

00:27:00.910 --> 00:27:02.660
Something like an engagement ring...

00:27:07.550 --> 00:27:10.420
Why did we prepare the exact same thing
at the exact same time?

00:27:10.540 --> 00:27:12.999
No, I've had this ready for a long time.

00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:14.130
No, me too.

00:27:14.670 --> 00:27:16.470
Then why now of all times?

00:27:16.590 --> 00:27:17.799
Today isn't even a special day.

00:27:17.800 --> 00:27:19.640
That's exactly why.

00:27:20.090 --> 00:27:21.370
That's what makes it a surprise.

00:27:26.640 --> 00:27:28.120
That wasn't cool at all.

00:27:29.330 --> 00:27:30.330
But still,

00:27:31.170 --> 00:27:32.620
this is so like us.

00:27:39.910 --> 00:27:40.910
Zen.

00:27:41.470 --> 00:27:42.470
Give me your hand.

00:27:56.920 --> 00:27:59.240
From now on... let's spend
the rest of our lives together,

00:28:02.030 --> 00:28:03.710
and keep competing in these silly matches.

00:28:05.970 --> 00:28:07.430
What a bizarre proposal.

00:28:08.550 --> 00:28:11.330
But it feels right for us. It feels real.

00:28:13.860 --> 00:28:18.070
Zen, didn't you tell me before
that you would make me happy?

00:28:20.250 --> 00:28:24.550
But I want us to be happy together.

00:28:25.890 --> 00:28:26.990
That kind of thing...

00:28:28.750 --> 00:28:30.550
Aren't we already
incredibly happy right now?

00:28:41.300 --> 00:28:44.220
To be worthy of being my partner,

00:28:44.390 --> 00:28:46.250
you'd better work hard.

00:28:48.110 --> 00:28:49.110
You too.

00:29:17.710 --> 00:29:19.670
This quarter is my victory.

00:29:22.720 --> 00:29:24.090
What's wrong?

00:29:24.430 --> 00:29:26.400
Making a sour face
like that isn't like you.

00:29:27.110 --> 00:29:31.069
I was just thinking
you're as clueless as ever.

00:29:31.070 --> 00:29:31.800
Huh?

00:29:31.850 --> 00:29:33.389
This is supposed to be a happy occasion.

00:29:33.390 --> 00:29:36.870
I bet you're going to say we should settle
this with our sales performance again anyway.

00:29:38.090 --> 00:29:39.090
Somehow,

00:29:39.210 --> 00:29:41.269
this scene has become so familiar.

00:29:41.270 --> 00:29:43.550
Yeah, but somehow,

00:29:44.010 --> 00:29:45.030
more than before...

00:29:45.950 --> 00:29:47.150
What is up with those two?

00:29:47.430 --> 00:29:48.869
Are they fighting again?

00:29:48.870 --> 00:29:49.890
Yeah.

00:29:50.490 --> 00:29:52.679
Even after they get married,

00:29:52.680 --> 00:29:54.320
they'll probably still be just like that.

00:29:55.710 --> 00:29:56.810
Who knows?

00:29:58.630 --> 00:30:01.419
You two, come help set up for the meeting.

00:30:01.420 --> 00:30:02.510
Sure.

00:30:07.050 --> 00:30:08.470
The remaining five...

00:30:10.630 --> 00:30:12.510
I'm going to make you
spill them all tonight.

00:30:13.390 --> 00:30:18.040
Sure. After all, the winner's word is law.

00:30:25.300 --> 00:30:31.800
"Fake Fact Lips"